catalogEntryView.shortDescription: A casual yet elegant sofa that offers comfort and modern styling to accent your home's living room.
catalogEntryView.longDescription: Modernize your living room space with the casual sofa. The sofa features cool tones, removable seat pillows, easy to clean polyester fabric, and an additional accent pillow along the backrest. The armchair's modern styling is complemented with durable brushed steel legs along its corners and center, for extra support. No assembly required.
catalogEntryView.name: Casual Sofa
